HEADWORD: Succussive
<hw>Suc*cus"sive</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Characterized by
a shaking motion, especially an up and down movement, and not merely
tremulous oscillation; <as>as, the <ex>succussive</ex> motion in
earthquakes</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

